caller_intent: Attempt to reach a specific extension (2352) for customer support or payment-related assistance.
resolution_steps: Automated system prompted caller to press numbers for different services.
Caller entered extension 2352, which was unavailable.
System instructed caller to leave a message after the tone.
knowledge_required: Understanding of automated phone menu systems
summary: Non-substantive outbound call to a North Carolina insurance association's automated system. Caller attempted to reach extension 2352 but was informed it was unavailable and directed to leave a voicemail. No agent interaction occurred.
